                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7506" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1882</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2700 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">突破增长“天花板”：科达制造的非洲国际化之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Breaking through the Growth &quot;Ceiling&quot;: KEDA&#39;s International Journey to Africa</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">欧阳桃花，龚克（通讯作者），牟晖，蔡家玮</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京航空航天大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科达制造股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际化战略；“一带一路”；进入海外市场模式与风险；传统制造业转型；价值增长；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Internationalization strategy; &quot;The Belt and Road&quot;; Entering overseas market models and risks; Transformation of traditional manufacturing industry; Value growth</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科达制造历经了30年发展，虽然已经成为亚洲第一，世界第二的陶瓷机械龙头企业，但触及到了行业“天花板”。为拓展新的业绩增长点，科达制造从2015年开始谋划非洲市场，布局建筑陶瓷业务、进入海外建材领域。至2022年底，科达制造在非洲的肯尼亚、加纳、坦桑尼亚、塞内加尔、赞比亚五国运营6个陶瓷工厂，营业收入从2017年的0.83亿元增长到2022年度的32.76亿元，年复合成长率为108.42%。非洲的建筑陶瓷业务的营收占集团总营收的三分之一。科达制造如何实现非洲国际化战略？本案例还原了传统制造企业科达制造拓展非洲市场，找到业务增长第二曲线的过程，可运用于企业进入海外市场动机、模式以及风险等相关知识点教学。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">After 30 years of development, KEDA has become the first leading ceramic machinery enterprise in Asia and the second leading ceramic machinery enterprise in the world, but it has touched the &quot;ceiling&quot; of the industry. In order to expand new performance growth points, KEDA began planning for the African market in 2015, expanding its architectural ceramics business and entering the overseas building materials field. By the end of 2022, KEDA has operated six ceramic factories in Kenya, Ghana, Tanzania, Senegal, and Zambia in Africa. Its operating revenue has increased from 83 million yuan in 2017 to 3.276 billion yuan in 2022, with a compound annual growth rate of 108.42%. The revenue of the architectural ceramics business in Africa accounts for one-third of the group&#39;s total revenue. How does KEDA achieve its internationalization strategy in Africa? This case restores the process of traditional manufacturing enterprise KEDA expanding into the African market and finding the second curve of business growth, which can be applied to teaching related knowledge points such as motivation, models, and risks for enterprises to enter overseas markets.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略管理》、《国际商务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&#183;实施国际化战略海外市场进入的动机：理解企业进入新市场的国际化的动机
&#183;实施国际化战略海外市场进入的模式：评估企业进入海外新市场的模式，以及各模式的优劣势
&#183;实施国际化战略海外市场进入的风险：分析企业国际化进入新市场过程中遇到的风险和管理方法
&#183;国际化战略选择：探讨未来的企业国际化战略选择</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
